#### Registering and Unregistering Aspects

To dynamically register and unregister aspects, we need to interact with Spring's AOP infrastructure. We'll use a `BeanFactoryPostProcessor` to register aspects.

```java
import org.springframework.beans.BeansException;
import org.springframework.beans.factory.config.BeanFactoryPostProcessor;
import org.springframework.beans.factory.config.ConfigurableListableBeanFactory;
import org.springframework.stereotype.Component;

@Component
public class AspectRegistry implements BeanFactoryPostProcessor {

    private DynamicAspectClassLoader classLoader;

    public AspectRegistry(DynamicAspectClassLoader classLoader) {
        this.classLoader = classLoader;
